# Caches
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache
**/.mypy_cache

# Tests are NOT copied into the runtime image. They are mounted by
# `make compose-test-kg` so unit tests stay byte-identical to source.
tests/
conftest.py

# Markdown docs except README.
*.md
!README.md

# Local dev cruft
.env
.env.local
*.log

# Editor
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Git internals never need to enter the build context
.git
.gitignore
